---
// src/components/Services.astro
---

<section class="py-24 px-6 bg-background">
  <div class="container max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <h2 
      data-animate
      class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-16 animate-on-scroll"
    >
      Servicios que transforman tu búsqueda de empleo
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
      <!-- Servicio 1 -->
      <div 
        data-animate
        class="bg-accent-secondary/20 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow animate-on-scroll"
      >
        <div class="bg-accent-main w-16 h-16 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-3 7h3m-3 4h3m-6-4h.01M9 16h.01" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-primary">CV Estratégico</h3>
        <p class="opacity-90">Transformamos tu currículum en un imán de entrevistas, destacando tus logros con métricas impactantes.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Servicio 2 -->
      <div 
        data-animate
        class="bg-accent-secondary/20 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow animate-on-scroll delay-150"
      >
        <div class="bg-accent-main w-16 h-16 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 10h.01M12 10h.01M16 10h.01M9 16H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v8a2 2 0 01-2 2h-5l-5 5v-5z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-primary">Entrenamiento de Entrevistas</h3>
        <p class="opacity-90">Dominamos juntos las preguntas difíciles y construimos respuestas convincentes que reflejen tu valor.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Servicio 3 -->
      <div 
        data-animate
        class="bg-accent-secondary/20 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow animate-on-scroll delay-300"
      >
        <div class="bg-accent-main w-16 h-16 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 12a9 9 0 01-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 00-9-9m9 9H3m9 9a9 9 0 01-9-9m9 9c1.657 0 3-4.03 3-9s-1.343-9-3-9m0 18c-1.657 0-3-4.03-3-9s1.343-9 3-9m-9 9a9 9 0 019-9" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-primary">Estrategia de Networking</h3>
        <p class="opacity-90">Te guiamos para construir conexiones genuinas con reclutadores y profesionales clave en tu industria.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Servicio 4 -->
      <div 
        data-animate
        class="bg-accent-secondary/20 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow animate-on-scroll delay-500"
      >
        <div class="bg-accent-main w-16 h-16 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-primary">Plan Personalizado</h3>
        <p class="opacity-90">Creamos una hoja de ruta única con objetivos semanales y tácticas adaptadas a tu mercado objetivo.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>